name: Two-tone cascade earring in red and white
description:
These are a pair of earrings in a two-toned cascading shade of red and white.

The motifs are made of cotton threads and held on to a fish hook earring.

The earring is made of high quality stainless steel which is nickel-free, hence causes no allergy to the skin.

The entire earring measures 2 inches in length and 1.5 inches in breadth.

name: Pure white fern motif earrings
description:
This is a pair of earring in fern shape in pure white color.

The diameter of each earring is 1 inches.

The pair comes perfect for daily wear or to complement a jazzy and colorful attire.

They are made from a fine cotton crochet thread, hence there is no chance of catching an allergy while wearing them. 

Also the earring hook is of the highest quality available in the market and is made up of steel which is nickel free. 

Hence the earring is ideally suited even for the most sensitive skin.

name: Two tone cascade earring
description:

The motifs are made of cotton threads and held on to a fish hook earring.

The earring is made of high quality stainless steel which is nickel-free, hence causes no allergy to the skin.

name: Tetra pack Recycled Wallet
description:
This is a sturdy water-proof wallet made by recycling a juice tetra-pack.

The wallet contains a currency pocket and 4 side-pockets for storing card money.

Among the 4 side-pockets there is also a pocket to store a photo-id and also has a velcro at the seam to secure it when closed.

The dimensions of the clutch are - 7.5 x 3 inches

An empty tetra-pack is washed thoroughly and  hand-sewn to form a wallet.

The product is sturdy enough to use everyday and creates a unique go green style statement.

name: Flower Charm Ring
description:
This is a handmade ring made by cotton crochet threads. The ring blank is of steel which is carefully covered with the same colored threads as the flower color. 

Wear this handmade ring and show some flower charm around.

The diameter of the flower is 1.5 inches, and the diameter of the ring is 3/4 inch.
